{
  "doc_id": "55448",
  "text": "Historically, OM approaches in businesses gradually have started to overlap with quality management, for example in lean management and six sigma (for definitions, see additional file 1, page 2-3). Research showed that promising approaches such as benchmarking, operations research, lean management and six sigma, can be adopted in healthcare [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] . However, concrete evidence is lacking whether these approaches developed especially for the manufacturing sector can also be used in healthcare [CITATION_6] .",
